\{ ans_rule(8) \}


$BR
$BR
$BBOLD Part e) $EBOLD
How many df are there for the standard error of 
any estimator \(\hat{\beta}\) of a parameter in the linear model? 
\{ ans_rule(6) \}


END_TEXT

